OL,3,CWelfare U-turn leaves a humiliated
OL,4,Cgovernment with a financial blackhole
OL,6,FThe government envisaged saving #4.5
OL,7,Fbillion a year by making it harder to
OL,8,Fqualify for Personal Independence
OL,9,FPayments.
OL,11,FAnd a further #2.7 billion by cutting
OL,12,Ffuture spending on incapacity benefit
OL,13,F- the "health" element of Universal
OL,14,FCredit.
