OL,3,CWelfare U-turn leaves a humiliated
OL,4,Cgovernment with a financial blackhole
OL,6,FThe government also wanted to increase
OL,7,Fthe generosity of universal credit for
OL,8,Fthose out of work without health
OL,9,Fproblems - benefit support for
OL,10,Fjobseekers in the UK is pretty mean by
OL,11,Fcomparison with other wealthy European
OL,12,Fnations.
OL,14,FThis netted out at total savings of
OL,15,F#5.5 billion by 2029/30.
OL,17,FThe PIP changes were tweaked and have
OL,18,Fnow been shelved.
OL,20,FThe changes to the incapacity benefit
OL,21,Fhave been watered down.
