OL,3,CWelfare U-turn leaves a humiliated
OL,4,Cgovernment with a financial blackhole
OL,6,FThe uplift to the standard allowance
OL,7,Fgoes ahead as planned, so savings are
OL,8,Fnow the sum total of zero.
OL,10,FAs things stand, the changes are
OL,11,Flikely to cost the government money.
OL,13,F"After (yesterday's) climbdown, the
OL,14,Fgovernment is effectively returning to
OL,15,Fthe drawing board," says Helen Miller
OL,16,Fof the Institute for Fiscal Studies.
