OL,3,CWelfare U-turn leaves a humiliated
OL,4,Cgovernment with a financial blackhole
OL,6,F"The Timms Review may lead to savings,
OL,7,Falthough Sir Stephen Timms, minister
OL,8,Fof state for social security and
OL,9,Fdisability, has said that the review
OL,10,Fis not intended to save money. And
OL,11,Fthis review is not due to report until
OL,12,Fautumn 2026."
OL,14,FLet us be clear, there has been a HUGE
OL,15,Fincrease in the number of people
OL,16,Fclaiming disability and incapacity
OL,17,Fbenefits in the last five years.
