OL,3,CWelfare U-turn leaves a humiliated
OL,4,Cgovernment with a financial blackhole
OL,6,FWe don't really know why. It's
OL,7,Fdefinitely not Long Covid. It's
OL,8,Fprobably not entirely down to the cost
OL,9,Fof living crisis, although higher
OL,10,Finflation will have been painful for
OL,11,Fanyone on benefits.
OL,13,FWe do know this hasn't happened in
OL,14,Fother countries.
OL,16,FIt's perfectly normal for a government
OL,17,Fto be concerned about a surge in
OL,18,Fclaims and to seek to reform the
OL,19,Fsystem, but goodness, this has been a
OL,20,Ffiasco.
