OL,3,CWelfare U-turn leaves a humiliated
OL,4,Cgovernment with a financial blackhole
OL,6,FThe outlook for economic growth (and
OL,7,Ftherefore tax revenues) is weak.
OL,8,FBorrowing is overshooting, and the
OL,9,Fgovernment's borrowing costs are high.
OL,10,FThe news doesn't look good.
OL,12,FAs things stand, there's a good chance
OL,13,FRachel Reeves will have to increase
OL,14,Ftaxes in the autumn, if she is still
OL,15,Fchancellor.
OL,17,FUnless something changes, there's the
OL,18,Fprospect of further political
OL,19,Fhumiliation ahead.
